snippet.title: Rusko feat. Amber Coffman "Hold On" [Music Video]
snippet.description:
Download/Stream: http://maddecent.fm/wooboostomg
Follow Mad Decent Weekly on Spotify: http://maddecent.fm/weeklyspotify

The official Mad Decent YouTube release of Rusko - Hold On. Stream the full track and other Rusko releases here or show support on iTunes or Google Play.

Buy Wake The Fuck Up shirts - http://bit.ly/crzKgh
The amazing new single featuring Amber Coffman gets an official video! Shot over a 5 day period of touring the UK, "Hold On" documents the chaotic life of one of dubsteps biggest acts. Directed by Jason Miller and Charles-Ryan for Eikon.

Grab Rusko's Brand New Album SONGS Out Now!
